            <thetext>We would like the generator to have a hierarchical search path.

For example:

framework 1
 I----enhanced framework 1

It means that if you point at &quot;enhanced framework 1&quot; it will look for files first there and then in &quot;framework 1&quot; to generate the code.

This helps a lot when developing for example qooxdoo-rtl and qooxdoo-titanium as examples. Both are dependent on qooxdoo and qooxdoo-mobile code.

The relation will be in better sync and be easier to maintain. No double copies of code not changed etc.

This must be quite easy to implement as it is only a lookup in respective config.json file to find if there is a parent framework it is built on.</thetext>
